              <history-note id="DLM138898"><amended-provision>Section 66(3A)</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>amended</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>1 June 2005</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM297136">section 206</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Corrections Act 2004</amending-leg> (2004 No 50).</history-note>
