          <history>
            <history-note id="DLM139608"><amended-provision>Section 107B</amended-provision>: <amending-operation>inserted</amending-operation>, on <amendment-date>7 July 2004</amendment-date>, by <amending-provision href="DLM304079">section 11</amending-provision> of the <amending-leg>Parole (Extended Supervision) Amendment Act 2004</amending-leg> (2004 No 67).</history-note>
